{lang-eng}Bhaktulara dhukka krantudu vache mahimatoda
Vijayadugaana moka rinchutaku poojyudu
Makhutamu talanchi abhisikthun jeyudu makutamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Paraloka marbhatimpa dhutalara kolvudi
Simhasanamunandu raju nabhisiktun cheyudi
Makutamu talanunchi rajarikamiyudi makutamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Papul mundla makuta meya garakshitu lellaru
Chuttu nilchi stutipaadi yesu perupondudi
Makutamu talanunchi jayamu prakatinchudi makutamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yesu mahonnathu dayen ha ! maha santoshamu
Arbhantinchu paata nvini goppaga stunchudi
Makutamu talanunchu dee rajadirajuku makutamu{/lang-eng}
